workflow:
apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: outfit-selection-workflow-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: checkweather
        template: checkweather
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: location
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.location }}'
      - name: dresssuggestion
        template: dresssuggestion
        dependencies:
        - checkweather
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: weather
            value: '{{ tasks.checkweather.result }}'
      - name: planoutfit
        template: planoutfit
        dependencies:
        - dresssuggestion
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: event
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.event }}'
          - name: outfit
            value: '{{ tasks.dresssuggestion.result }}'

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: movie-booking-workflow-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: bookmovieticket
        template: bookmovieticket
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: movie_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
          - name: showtime
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.showtime }}'
          - name: number_of_tickets
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.number_of_tickets }}'
  - name: bookmovieticket
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/bookmovieticket"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "movie_name": "{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}",
          "showtime": "{{ inputs.parameters.showtime }}",
          "number_of_tickets": {{ inputs.parameters.number_of_tickets }}
        }
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: movie_name
      value: 'Inception'
    - name: showtime
      value: '8pm'
    - name: number_of_tickets
      value: '1'

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: movie-ticket-booking-
spec:

    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: getmovietheaters
        template: getmovietheaters
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: city
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.city }}'
      - name: buymovieticket
        template: buymovieticket
        dependencies:
        - getmovietheaters
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: movie_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
          - name: theater_name
            value: '{{ tasks.getmovietheaters.result }}'
          - name: date
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.date }}'
          - name: time
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.time }}'
  templates:
  - name: getmovietheaters
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: city
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/getmovietheaters"
      method: "GET"
  - name: buymovieticket
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: movie_name
      - name: theater_name
      - name: date
      - name: time
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/buymovieticket"
      method: "POST"

        dependencies:

        arguments:
          parameters:

            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.cinema }}'
          - name: movie
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie }}'
          - name: show_time
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.show_time }}'
  - name: checkavailability
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: cinema
      - name: showtimes
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/checkavailability"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
      - name: "Content-Type"
        value: "application/json"
      body: "{}"
  - name: bookticket
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: cinema_name
      - name: movie
      - name: show_time
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/bookticket"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
      - name: "Content-Type"
        value: "application/json"
      body: "{}"

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: travel-booking-workflow-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: getweather
        template: getweather
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: city
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.destination }}'
          - name: date
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.start_date }}'
      - name: findflight
        template: findflight
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: cityDeparture
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.cityDeparture }}'
          - name: cityArrival
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.destination }}'
          - name: date
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.start_date }}'
      - name: findhotel
        template: findhotel
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: city
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.destination }}'
      - name: hotelbooking
        template: hotelbooking
        dependencies:
        - findhotel
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: destination
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.destination }}'
          - name: check_in_date
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.start_date }}'
          - name: check_out_date
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.end_date }}'
      - name: besttraveltime
        template: besttraveltime
        dependencies:
        - getweather
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: weather_condition
            value: '{{ tasks.getweather.result }}'
          - name: attraction
            value: 'sightseeing'
      - name: itineraryplanner
        template: itineraryplanner
        dependencies:
        - findflight
        - hotelbooking
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: flight_details
            value: '{{ tasks.findflight.result }}'
          - name: hotel_booking
            value: '{{ tasks.hotelbooking.result }}'
